the first half at the smith center
guard phil ford set from 1974 to 1978
gene hansbrough , who surprised his son by attending the game
hansbrough , who accepted the game ball and an embrace from ford , now an assistant coach for the nba 's charlotte bobcats
hansbrough , who also grabbed nine rebounds
fans in the sellout crowd -- some of whom held signs reading '' phil ford 2,290 '' on one side and '' tyler 2,291 + '' on the other --
then hansbrough -- who followed his record-breaking bucket with a missed dunk attempt that probably will make the team blooper reel --
unc 's chart for all-time free-throw attempts
the nba scoring record -- boy , that 's going to be hard
